WEBVTT

1
01:09:05.200 --> 01:09:06.730 
南非模式
Shades of South Africa.

2
01:09:07.000 --> 01:09:08.100 
不尽然
Not quite.

3
01:09:08.510 --> 01:09:10.060 
现在只是拘留
They're only holding me...

4
01:09:10.270 --> 01:09:12.370 
要到本县县长审问后
...until the magistrate's hearing.

5
01:09:12.580 --> 01:09:14.370 
才是坐牢
Then it will be prison.

6
01:09:17.310 --> 01:09:19.110 
他们拿走你的衣物了
Did they take your clothes?

7
01:09:20.580 --> 01:09:22.310 
现在起我的衣服就是这些了
These are my clothes now.

8
01:09:24.220 --> 01:09:27.310 
你一向有清教徒的倾向
You always had a puritanical streak.

